<plot>Leila's a woman who fears love due to a tragic experience that occurred while she was enjoying her passion - salsa. The experience not only closed her heart, but it extinguished her desire for the dance. Years later, Leila is literally living in this state of mind at the coffee shop where she works. The place remains cold and empty, just like she is emotionally. One day, an eccentric yet charming stranger, Robbie, steps off a bus and into her life with one goal -- to get into her heart before it's too late. By reconnecting her to the art and passion of dance she loves, he helps her find the courage to come to terms with her inner demons and reopen her heart.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?328923</url></doc>
